TOON (Token-Oriented Object Notation)
--------------------------------------
A proprietary agent optimization layer for compressing documentation into
token-efficient JSON format for AI agent consumption.

Principal Developer: William Finger
Copyright Holder: William Finger
Development Period: 2025

Key innovations include:
- Hierarchical stack-based markdown parser with nested section preservation
- Multi-line list item parsing with continuation tracking
- Token-aware compression algorithms (60-85% token reduction)
- Path traversal prevention and security hardening
- Glob pattern matching for selective file discovery


